'''烟酰氯'''，也称'''3-吡啶甲酰氯'''，是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>ClNO。

==合成==
烟酰氯可由烟酸钾和[[草酰氯|草酰氯]]在无水苯中反应得到。<ref name=Wingfield>{{cite journal|last1=Wingfield|first1=H. N.|last2=Harlan|first2=W. R.|last3=Hanmer|first3=H. R.|title=The Preparation of Nicotinyl Chloride|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=75|issue=17|year=1953|pages=4364–4364|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/ja01113a530}}</ref>[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]也可用作酰氯化试剂进行反应，<ref name=orgsyn>{{cite journal|title=3-benzoylpyridine|journal=Organic Syntheses|volume=37|year=1957|pages=6|issn=00786209|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.037.0006}}</ref>其它可用溶剂有[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]<ref>Zinner, Helmut; Fiedler, Heinz. Nicotinic acid phenol esters with antimycotic and hyperemic-​like activity. ''Archiv der Pharmazie und Berichte der Deutschen Pharmazeutischen Gesellschaft'', 1958. 291/63. 330-338. ISSN: 0376-0367.</ref>、[[二氯甲烷|二氯甲烷]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Chen|first1=Yang|last2=Liu|first2=Yu|last3=Zhang|first3=Xiao|last4=Lu|first4=Da|last5=Yang|first5=Lixin|last6=Deng|first6=Junfeng|last7=Deng|first7=Shengqi|title=Copper Catalyzed Direct Synthesis of Nitriles from Acyl Azides|journal=ChemistrySelect|volume=3|issue=43|year=2018|pages=12325–12329|issn=2365-6549|doi=10.1002/slct.201802918}}</ref>等，[[N,N-二甲基甲酰胺|''N'',''N''-二甲基甲酰胺]]可用作反应的催化剂<ref>Priya, B. S., Basappa, Nanjunda Swamy, S., & Rangappa, K. S. (2005). Synthesis and characterization of novel 6-fluoro-4-piperidinyl-1,2-benzisoxazole amides and 6-fluoro-chroman-2-carboxamides: antimicrobial studies. Bioorganic & Medicinal Chemistry, 13(7), 2623–2628. {{doi|10.1016/j.bmc.2005.01.026}}</ref>。
