==性质==
烟酰氯在潮湿空气中水解，生成[[烟酰氯盐酸盐|烟酰氯盐酸盐]]。<ref name=Wingfield />它和醇反应生成酯，如和无水[[乙醇|乙醇]]反应，生成烟酸乙酯<ref name=Wingfield />；和胺反应生成[[酰胺|酰胺]]，如和[[4-甲基苯胺|4-甲基苯胺]]在二氯甲烷中反应，生成(4-甲基苯基)-3-烟酰胺。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Mocilac|first1=Pavle|last2=Gallagher|first2=John F.|title=Structural systematics and conformational analyses of a 3 × 3 isomer grid of nine N-(tolyl)pyridinecarboxamides and three chlorinated relatives|journal=CrystEngComm|volume=13|issue=17|year=2011|pages=5354|issn=1466-8033|doi=10.1039/c1ce05169e}}</ref>它和肼反应，可以生成[[烟酰肼|烟酰肼]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ramalakshmi|first1=N.|last2=Aruloly|first2=L. |last3=Arunkumar|first3= S. |last4=Ilango|first4=K. |last5=Puratchikody|first5=A. |title=Synthesis and Biological Evaluation of Some Novel Nicotinic Acid Derivatives|journal=Malaysian Journal of Science|volume=28|issue=2|year=2009|pages=197–203|issn=13943065|doi=10.22452/mjs.vol28no2.8}}</ref>或''N'',''N'''-二烟酰肼<ref>Pamar, Malavath Geeta; Gannimani, Ramesh; Govender, Patrick; Ramjugernath, Deresh; Nanjundaswamy, Hemmaragala Marishetty. Rapid generation of N,​N'-​diacylhydrazines by I2 or Br2​/hydrazine hydrate: a facile route to 1,​3,​4-​oxadiazoles. ''Organic Chemistry: An Indian Journal'', 2014. 10 (1): 17-23. ISSN: 0974-7516.</ref>。

在三氯化铝的存在下，烟酰氯也能和[[苯|苯]]反应，生成3-苯甲酰基吡啶。<ref name=orgsyn />
